  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Support the ongoing development of one of the hottest modern paintball games to hit the market in over a decade. Aiming to simulate tournament style paintball, Infinite Tournament Paintball captures the highly competitive nature of paintball in an action packed digital counterpart. We are constantly updating features, gameplay elements and adding new gear. Just check out the news section of the Infinite community hub!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341160/extras/c825aa8b8f60f2fddfa30e43050cb888.avif?t=1755462901\" width=616 height=192 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle your friends</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in online matches up to 5v5. Whether you host your own server or join a public lobby, you're sure to have a good time slinging digital paint online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341160/extras/d9d2c4ed2e4f9ef73cb64d101fe19428.avif?t=1755462901\" width=616 height=192 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Test your skills against  AI Players in Exhibition Mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sharpen up your skills on the field with the Infinite AI players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341160/extras/d881a43aea2c585c9dd347dcc8500164.avif?t=1755462901\" width=616 height=192 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay that is fun while staying true to tournament paintball</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infinite aims to strike the perfect balance between gameplay and realism. Featuring X-Ball format gameplay, 10.5 BPS ramping, hand swapping, snapping, sliding, diving and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341160/extras/558d85fe3488cba64d223e6aeeb44e49.avif?t=1755462901\" width=616 height=192 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Scaled Layouts</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All layouts are scale 1 to 1 to their real life counterparts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341160/extras/c55138c74c3b88679d756f8eadc05af6.avif?t=1755462901\" width=616 height=192 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with your favorite gear</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We've teamed up with multiple companies to bring a catalogue of real  gear into Infinite with more being added regularly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>- Built almost entirely on feedback from the community ranging from casual ballers, to true professionals</strong></u><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong></strong></u><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>- Join the community Discord along side 4,500+ members to find team mates and share your ideas for the game  </u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong></strong></u><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>- Take advantage of free content updates</strong></u></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Support the ongoing development of one of the hottest modern paintball games to hit the market in over a decade. Aiming to simulate tournament style paintball, Infinite Tournament Paintball captures the highly competitive nature of paintball in an action packed digital counterpart. We are constantly updating features, gameplay elements and adding new gear. Just check out the news section of the Infinite community hub!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341160/extras/c825aa8b8f60f2fddfa30e43050cb888.avif?t=1755462901\" width=616 height=192 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle your friends</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in online matches up to 5v5. Whether you host your own server or join a public lobby, you're sure to have a good time slinging digital paint online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341160/extras/d9d2c4ed2e4f9ef73cb64d101fe19428.avif?t=1755462901\" width=616 height=192 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Test your skills against  AI Players in Exhibition Mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sharpen up your skills on the field with the Infinite AI players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341160/extras/d881a43aea2c585c9dd347dcc8500164.avif?t=1755462901\" width=616 height=192 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay that is fun while staying true to tournament paintball</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infinite aims to strike the perfect balance between gameplay and realism. Featuring X-Ball format gameplay, 10.5 BPS ramping, hand swapping, snapping, sliding, diving and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341160/extras/558d85fe3488cba64d223e6aeeb44e49.avif?t=1755462901\" width=616 height=192 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Scaled Layouts</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All layouts are scale 1 to 1 to their real life counterparts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341160/extras/c55138c74c3b88679d756f8eadc05af6.avif?t=1755462901\" width=616 height=192 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with your favorite gear</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We've teamed up with multiple companies to bring a catalogue of real  gear into Infinite with more being added regularly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>- Built almost entirely on feedback from the community ranging from casual ballers, to true professionals</strong></u><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong></strong></u><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>- Join the community Discord along side 4,500+ members to find team mates and share your ideas for the game  </u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong></strong></u><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>- Take advantage of free content updates</strong></u></p>",
